---
title: Creamy Poppy Seed & Chicken Pasta with Spinach
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Poppy Seeds and Chicken Pasta in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-poppy-seed-chicken-pasta-64525d37-83c2ee4a.jpg
